'''Hudi Bitek''' ({{IPA-sh|xûːdi bîtek|hr}}) is a village on the outskirts of [[Zagreb]], [[Croatia]]. It is administratively located in the [[Brezovica, Zagreb|Brezovica]] city district. The population is 331.<ref>http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/censuses/Census2001/Popis/E01_01_03/e01_01_03_zup22-00.html</ref> Hudi Bitek has been an inhabited settlement since the [[medieval]] times.<ref name="iz povijesti">{{cite web | url = http://www.zagreb.hr/default.aspx?id=14485 | title = Iz povijesti | accessdate = 2016-10-29 | work = zagreb.hr | publisher = City of Zagreb | language = Croatian }}</ref>
