{{Infobox Political post |post = Mayor |body = [[Yerevan]] |image = |incumbent = [[Hayk Marutyan]] |incumbentsince = October 13, 2018 |style = |residence = [[Yerevan City Hall]] |termlength = Five years, renewable |formation = 1879 |succession = |salary = |inaugural = Hovhannes Ghorghanyan |website = [https://www.yerevan.am/en/mayor/ Official website] |flag = Yerevan flag.gif |flagcaption = [[Flag of Yerevan]] |flagsize = 130px |native_name = {{native name|hy|Երևանի քաղաքապետ}} |appointer = [[Yerevan City Council]] }}
The '''Mayor of Yerevan''' ({{Lang-hy|Երևանի քաղաքապետ}}) is head of the executive branch of [[Yerevan]]'s government. He is elected by the [[Yerevan City Council]]. Recent [[Yerevan City Council election, 2018|city council elections took place in 2018]], [[Yerevan City Council election, 2017|2017]] and [[Yerevan City Council election, 2013|2013]].
